  <brief_title>Effects of Volatile and Intravenous Anesthetics on Pupillary Function</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Effects of Volatile and Intravenous Anesthetics on Pupillary Function During General Anesthesia in Children; a Prospective Observational Study.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Seoul National University Hospital</agency>
