  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare of effects of volatile and intravenous anesthetics on pupillary function during&#xD;
      general anesthesia in children&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigator will measure the pupillary function with pupillometry during general&#xD;
      anesthesia with volatile or intravenous anesthetics in children.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
