  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        From other study results, average NPi for Sevoflurane and propofol were 3.6, 4.2, and&#xD;
        standard deviation was 0.1, 0.4 respectively. Using Gpower program, total of 18 patients&#xD;
        were required. Considering 20% of drop-out rate, total of 22 patients(18+3.6 patients) were&#xD;
        to be recruited.&#xD;
      </textblock>
